                  </hi>. I sell books, and live in Fleet-street. On the 28th of September, on receiving information, I went out, and saw a person like the prisoner running across the road—I saw him drop this book, which is mine—I took it up—I believe the prisoner to be the person, but he was not taken in my sight.</p>
